[B]Ok, now that i have 2 ssoys, i find that i'm often out of stamina when meleeing 2 or more 40+ mobs down.  I was always under the impression that your attack speed went down when you run out of stamina, but in another post, several people thought otherwise.  Does anybody have proof that no stamina affects damage/atk speed at all?  This will have implications for all dual wielding melee types who don't have massive stamina like ogres.  It'll also affect stamina draining zones such as kedge.
[/B][/QUOTE]

